asked somewhere along here is, are you

39:51.638 --> 39:57.685
cooperating at this point With University of 
Texas, is there any collusion in the sense of joint

39:58.947 --> 40:07.759
planning and development? I wouldn't say there 
was joint planning, particularly. We try to

40:11.424 --> 40:16.992
collaborate pretty closely in the legislative 
session. Which is really relevant to new

40:17.813 --> 40:19.795
development, too. It is. But Cunningham and I at 
Shilkin Lawless have been kind of a coalition of

40:26.268 --> 40:29.431
the big dogs, if you will. And we've met frequently 
and coordinated different kinds of activities.

