Of course, a uniform difficult challenge in these 
times is the financial one. So dealing with the

42:38.214 --> 42:52.999
legislature in particular, the state 
legislature, and trying to be sure that we get our

42:38.214 --> 42:52.999
share of the funding, that is one of the most 
difficult challenges.

